Quantum Hilbert Space Tensors

Author: Dan Stahlke
License: BSD

Installation:
	./setup.py test
	sudo ./setup.py install

	# If you have Sage:
	cd sage_package
	rm -f qitensor-*.spkg
	./build-sage-package.sh
	sage -f qitensor-*.spkg

Web page: http://www.stahlke.org/dan/qitensor

Documentation:
	View documentation online at:
		http://www.stahlke.org/dan/qitensor/doc/index.html
	
	If you have the full source from git, you can build your own
	set of documentation:
		cd doc
		make html
		firefox _build/html/index.html

Testing:
	This assumes you have the full source code from git.

	./setup.py test

	cd doc
	make clean
	make doctest
	cd ..

	cd sage_package
	rm -f qitensor-*.spkg
	./build-sage-package.sh
	sage -f qitensor-*.spkg
	cd ../doc/examples
	# This takes a while (almost a minute)
	./run-all-sage-tests.sh
